{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram — Conditional checkout shipping-address prefill config (Phase 2.11F.2 → 2.12B).

  Publishes window.GanguramCheckoutPrefillConfig and loads
  assets/ganguram-checkout-prefill.js. On the STANDARD checkout button it appends the
  documented checkout[shipping_address][...] params. CONDITIONAL modes (from
  window.GanguramAddress): a manual pincode -> country + zip ONLY; a selected full Google
  address -> country + zip + address1 + city + province. Never sends stale/guessed data.

  Standard checkout button only (Shop Pay / dynamic buttons bypass the cart form — they
  can't be prefilled this way). DATE SAFETY: does nothing while checkout is blocked, INCLUDING
  when a required cart-page delivery date is missing — so it can't bypass that step. Preserves
  cart / attributes / discounts / payment. Fail-open. Set enabled:false to turn it off. No
  checkout-rate / ShipZip / SBZ / zipLogic / resolver / MOV / estimate / settings_data change.
{%- endcomment -%}
<script>
  window.GanguramCheckoutPrefillConfig = {
    // Phase 2.12B — ON, and SAFE for a cart-page date picker: the prefill does nothing while
    // checkout is blocked, INCLUDING when a required delivery date is missing
    // (GanguramDeliveryDatePicker.isDateMissing), so the redirect can't bypass the date step.
    enabled: true,
    checkoutUrl: "/checkout",
    defaultCountry: "India"
  };
</script>
<script src="{{ 'ganguram-checkout-prefill.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
